      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not a state of mind though. it's just reality. the money is gone, the life i built is gone. there's no \"climbing out\" when the ground itself is gone. i just feel so tired of trying to find a reason to keep going when everything is just zero. it feels more honest to just accept that it's over.",
